-- Japan's SMFG raises H1 net profit estimate by 39 pct
-- By Chris Gallagher
-- Mon Sep 29, 2014 03:17AM EDT
-- None



TOKYO, Sept 29 (Reuters) - Sumitomo Mitsui Financial Group Inc <8316.T> on Monday raised its net profit estimate for the fiscal first half by 39 percent, bolstered by earnings at its core banking unit and gains stemming from unused loan loss provisions.

